34
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:26,760
It may be reviewed by other researchers or lie unrespected.

35
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:32,360
There you can compare with Wikipedia, where everyone writes and reviews each other.

36
00:02:32,440 --> 00:02:35,640
But one can get into Wikipedia where it is not reviewed-

37
00:02:35,720 --> 00:02:39,160
-or in a subject that is controversial, with several opinions.

38
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:43,680
But if you know how things work, you can use them properly.

39
00:02:43,760 --> 00:02:48,160
You can write: The material is not reviewed, but I want to address it anyway.

40
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:51,960
It is an important point in having knowledge of open access.

41
00:02:52,040 --> 00:02:57,640
Another thing is that you who write the material that is openly available ...

42
