44
00:03:08,160 --> 00:03:13,480
They have written away their copyright, the right to spread their material.

45
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:19,160
Now you talk about open licenses where researchers retain their copyright.

46
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:25,560
Here, too, knowledge is required to know what license to put, what suits it.

47
00:03:25,640 --> 00:03:30,560
It is important for those who manufacture resources or write the material-

48
00:03:30,640 --> 00:03:35,080
